---
import { MdOutlineQuiz } from "react-icons/md";
---

<section id="quiz" class="scroll-my-24">
  <div class="py-24 px-5 text-white bg-dark-blue relative overflow-hidden">
    <MdOutlineQuiz
      className="size-[40rem] right-16 -top-8 text-white/10 absolute"
    />
    <div class="max-w-xl lg:max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="uppercase text-mustard-yellow font-bold tracking-widest">
          Become a Pilot
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">Ready to Take Off?</h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 leading-loose my-5">
          Thinking about learning to fly but not sure where to begin? You’re not
          alone, and the first step is easier than you might think. At High Tide
          Aviation, we created a quick and practical Flight Training Readiness
          Assessment to help you understand what’s involved in earning your
          wings.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 leading-loose my-5">
          Whether you're in Southport, NC, Wilmington, NC, or St. Simons Island,
          GA, complete the assessment and get <strong
            class="text-mustard-yellow"
            >15% off your next Discovery Flight</strong
          > as our way of helping you take that exciting first step.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/quiz-form"
          class="btn-yellow mt-4 inline-block text-lg font-semibold"
        >
          Take the Assessment & Claim 15% Off
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
